# Description

This is an Alfred 2 workflow that makes it easy to manage VPN connection.

# Usage

0. Construct VPN service with System Preferences.app 
1. Type `vpn` into Alfred followed by a space.
2. Begin typing the name of the device you want to switch VPN service.
3. When you see the service you want, select it from the list as usual.
4. Press return to switch the service.

# Installation

Download latest `alfred-switch-vpn.alfredworkflow` from
[Release page](https://github.com/uchida/alfred-switch-vpn/releases).
Open `alfred-switch-vpn.alfredworkflow` with Alfred.

